{
  "stem": "19895.8",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And no country I seen beside Hungary, at that point, except during my little excursion into the concentration camp on the Austrian border.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was very interested about the west.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said to this lady, says, the story tells, my mother tells that we have some relatives who survived World War II.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They are German part of the family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And somebody lives in London.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Do you mind if I ask you, when you go back to London, pick up the phone book and see you if there is a Schleyer in the book.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She says, I sure will do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So time goes by.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The revolution breaks out in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the confusion of a revolution and of these days, mail is not daily delivered, but somehow, some mail is delivered.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what comes on the mail, a letter from London.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this relative, distant relative, second cousin of my mother, an elderly man, who lives in London by the name of-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I forgot this, only the first name.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyhow, writes to me and writes in German that he's very happy to hear that my mother, and I, and my father survived World War II.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in this terrible time of-- of the revolution in Hungary, which they know about, he would like to see that if I ever get out of the country, or visiting, or whatever, he would like to meet me and let them know.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was an unusual letter [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and an interesting coincidence.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it comes the day that I decide to escape from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't want to go into details that escaping was crossing the border on foot.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
